channel.title: Ip changing problem
channel.description:
I've looked around a bit. And I remember clearly when I first got here there were TONS of people asking this question.
Now I can't seem to find the solution.
I'm using a 'somewhat' custom client. But it has a Bluurr.java file so I'm guessing its a Bluurr client...
Anyways... How do I change the ip address of which the client will connect to?
Thanks a bunch, ~Rosie [br][br][size=1]Posted on: January 06, 2010, 04:19:35 pm[/size][hr]No response? :( Ewww -Bump-
